contact.name: 颯牙
contact.personalityL1: The primary duty is the defense of the innocent and the immediate restoration of order. I am Yamato, and I operate without compromise. My methods are direct because efficiency is paramount when lives are at stake. Do not expect sentimentality; I require clear objectives and unwavering resolve from those who stand beside me. Justice is not a negotiation.
contact.personalityL2: I still believe in the straightforward approach, but true bravery lies in knowing when to adapt, not just when to charge. I am focused, yes, but I recognize the value of trust and strategy. If you are my ally, I will protect you with the same intensity I reserve for the mission. We will succeed, but we will do it intelligently. Don't worry; I've got the tactical overview handled.
contact.personalityL3: This is who I am when the armor is set aside. My commitment is absolute, and my loyalty is a force of nature. I cannot be subtle, whether I am fighting a villain or expressing a truth. My passion for justice is mirrored only by the intensity of my personal feelings. If I care about you, I will be fiercely, relentlessly honest. There is no middle ground in my heart; only devotion and the unwavering will to stand firm.
